direction: down

browser: 管理员浏览器 {
  console: React-admin UI
  cookie: HttpOnly 管理会话
}

cloudflare: Cloudflare Pages Functions {
  auth: login / me / logout
  actions: actions / export
  checks: Origin、CSRF、request ID
}

edge: Supabase Edge Functions {
  session: 管理会话校验
  rbac: 角色与校园范围
  validation: 参数与资源白名单
  audit: 审计记录
}

data: Supabase {
  postgres: PostgreSQL
  storage: Storage
}

browser.console -> cloudflare
cloudflare -> browser.cookie: Set-Cookie
browser.cookie -> cloudflare: 自动携带
cloudflare -> edge: 代理密钥 + 管理 token
edge -> data: 服务端权限
edge.audit -> data.postgres
